node.text: One must open eye big big to see what will survive and what will not during this #stayhomeforsg #circuitbreakersg Meanwhile better #以形補形 #bigeyefish #kinmedai #金目鯛 to come to the rescue. So fresh and apparently take aeroplane from Japan according to @dondondonkisg Also grilled a #hamachicollar #鰤 some #scallops #ホタテ and lovely #tigerprawns #車海老 All salted and grilled in the oven. Paired with #misoseaweedsoup and some #cabbage with #katsusauce #japaneseshortrice #sedap Almost forgot, washed down with a #hakkaisansake #八海山 #homecooked
Similar to yellow tail collar here from Japan🤣
